《'''杰·雷诺的车库'''》（{{lang-en|''Jay Leno's Garage''}}）是一档以机动车为主题的美国电视节目，由《[[今夜秀|今夜秀]]》前主持人[[杰·雷诺|杰·雷诺]]担纲主持。节目主要关注各种汽车、摩托车，包括老爷车和改装车，有时会邀请特殊嘉宾一起点评、体验甚至飙车。节目中出现的嘉宾包括美国总统[[乔治·沃克·布什|乔治·沃克·布什]]<ref>{{Cite news | url = https://fordauthority.com/2020/07/jay-leno-takes-a-spin-in-george-w-bushs-f-150-king-ranch-video/ | title = Jay Leno Takes A Spin in George W. Bush’s F-150 King Ranch: Video | work = Ford | date = 2020-07-30 | accessdate = 2021-02-09 | archive-date = 2021-01-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210105023814/https://fordauthority.com/2020/07/jay-leno-takes-a-spin-in-george-w-bushs-f-150-king-ranch-video/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>、[[乔·拜登|乔·拜登]]<ref>{{Cite news | url = https://www.cnbc.com/2016/11/10/joe-biden-and-colin-powell-drag-race-67-corvettes.html | title = Joe Biden and Colin Powell drag race their ’67 and 2015 Corvettes | date = 2016-11-10 | accessdate = 2021-02-09 | archive-date = 2021-01-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210125174128/https://www.cnbc.com/2016/11/10/joe-biden-and-colin-powell-drag-race-67-corvettes.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>、美国首富[[伊隆·马斯克|伊隆·马斯克]]<ref>{{Cite news | url = https://www.theverge.com/2020/5/28/21273140/jay-leno-elon-musk-tesla-cybertruck-boring-company-tunnel | title = Jay Leno drives Tesla’s Cybertruck through Elon Musk’s Boring Company tunnel | work = The Verge | date = 2020-05-28 | accessdate = 2021-02-09 | archive-date = 2021-03-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210309010538/https://www.theverge.com/2020/5/28/21273140/jay-leno-elon-musk-tesla-cybertruck-boring-company-tunnel | dead-url = no }}</ref>等。《杰·雷诺的车库》原本于2014年在[[全国广播公司|全国广播公司]]（{{lang|en|NBC}}）网站以及[[消费者新闻与商业频道|消费者新闻与商业频道]]（{{lang|en|CNBC}}）上播出<ref>{{cite news|title=Late-Night Legend Jay Leno Drives to CNBC Primetime|url=https://www.cnbc.com/id/102089424|access-date=May 21, 2015|work=CNBC (News Release)|date=October 14, 2014|archive-date=2015-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150509114409/http://www.cnbc.com/id/102089424|dead-url=no}}</ref>，后来在2015年成为一档每周更新的黄金档节目，截止到2020年已更新5季节目。<ref name=garageuso>{{cite news|title=It's Official: Jay Leno Hosting Primetime CNBC Series|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/official-jay-leno-hosting-primetime-740970|access-date=May 21, 2015|work=The Hollywood Reporter|date=October 14, 2014|archive-date=2021-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210213003803/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/official-jay-leno-hosting-primetime-740970|dead-url=no}}</ref>

